title: 09/21: Mailbag (Recorded Fri. Before the AB News)
description:
Recorded prior to Antonio Brown's release, we answer your trade and start/sit questions while doing some Regulating as well. Plus some injury updates as Marlon Mack practiced and Damien Williams is out.
